name: Edunow
body:
### Welcome to EDUMEETUP
The education of the next century is enabled by edumeetup: the new meetup for educational purposes. Come back soon to get to know it!

### Authors and Contributors
Edumeetup is a project ideated by Israel Gutiérrez (@gootyfer).

### Support or Contact
Wanna learn more? Contact us at info@edumeetup.com and we’ll come to you sortly.
